{"tid":1724351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［打氣］應承我，一齊願榮光歸香港好唔好？","createTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:55:00.000Z","uid":101022,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea021cfd31284bdc52e7fa08018f47713203a04","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"我地<span style=\"color: orange;\">打咗5個月</span>為咩？咁多手足為我地賠償左自己條命、工作、金錢、時間、精神、最愛既人又係為咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建自由光輝香港</span></span>啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢兩三日，大家啲團結、勇氣、智慧去曬邊？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一邊有人捉鬼、互相指責，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一邊有人怕左，無再出黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉頭又有人盲目，一意孤行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足，我地唔好<span style=\"color: gold;\">比支共分化成功</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地有<span style=\"color: green;\">有文化、有修養、受過高等教育</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">民主既群體</span>！<br />\n<br />\n過往五個月，每一次運動有樽頸位，我地都有創意、同埋智慧咁樣逐一衝破！每一次雖然有人流淚、人流血、有人犧牲，但係我哋吶喊、向前邁進嘅聲音，仍然係無停過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍自由 - 來齊集這裏，來團結抗對，勇氣、智慧也永不滅！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋每次要對抗嘅，唔單只係支共既卑鄙手段，仲有自己各種嘅情緒，我相信只要我哋衝破左，我地香港人一定可以贏呢一場仗，將<span style=\"color: violet;\">民主、自由</span>，真真正正帶入呢個家園！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n點都好！<br />\n不篤灰、不分化、不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶住已犧牲、有名無名手足既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n化傷痛、憤怒、黎明嘅盼望為力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目光對準政暴力詭詐嘅政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅持我哋<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應承我，</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n願榮光歸香港！</span>好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"de563eb8728030a573240ee3e0b3195da06a2ad0","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d83e61b4ab62da5af778e91af7f2e80571f4d7c","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"839d21cffaa281540d5e8ace1aafde734074a98d","tid":1724351,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d9c435367f5f8bbc1859a0f8ef4c07bd5121f8","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a14d89ada0c1f169c572c176d76c044dcd91b1b","tid":1724351,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47c66e59ec2d80b9d180b6b43d38a1713758cf8b","tid":1724351,"uid":56633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"344b2182b01a87c50d3b48220040e5d7a3ae09ce","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"172de1183281ff579602dd093a0a6fa03ee97c8c","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6ac3927df2c25928800c74d34c9c26d38f33c44","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"何以這土地淚再流"},{"pid":"3b09cd93d3f4271aa0598720c744d160d33c82fe","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"何以叫眾人亦憤恨"},{"pid":"0a58129ee3a60b1239b9a633a9996630fcc49159","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲響透"},{"pid":"46755d76e3dbcc9e67019d9c167c00316ad0a002","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c327d783d8d4016b948d37fca4899d1649232f00","tid":1724351,"uid":134450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"推，堅持啊咁多位"},{"pid":"08277a2888f6c422d865a1ef33064ef6836d8582","tid":1724351,"uid":83283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b33733c199e61ebc451d718bed697b93b62ef40","tid":1724351,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}